  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objectives of the data search is to find out if there is correlation between pre, post
      serum sodium concentration, dialysate sodium concentration, interdialytic weight gain and
      associated changes in pre and post systolic and diastolic blood pressure, mean arterial
      pressure, number of blood pressure medications and adherence to 3 times per week dialysis,
      mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
